{"tid":2416199,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–癌細胞嗜糖的原因","createTime":"2021-02-20T22:05:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-22T07:10:08.000Z","uid":38861,"like":77,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"ecd36d2be8cc210606cbd825be943d7247ce1f76","tid":2416199,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T22:05:51.000Z","msg":"癌細胞經常被描繪為極度嗜糖。的而且確，大部份的癌細胞對比同等類型的正常細胞均會攝取更多的糖份。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d9RpfpA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd9RpfpA.jpg&h=a72cb0dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n箇中的原因至少有三:<br />\n1.致癌基因的表達率增加<br />\n2.新陳代謝酶素變異<br />\n3.周遭環境缺乏氧氣<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）沒有氧氣的話，脂肪及氨基酸並不能轉化成為可供細胞所用的能源。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nQifm4D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnQifm4D.jpg&h=316d586e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然而，糖份在擁有氧氣或缺乏氧氣的情況下，均可轉化成為能源。<br />\n因此，當癌細胞處於缺氧狀態的時候，便會增加對糖份的依賴。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）正常的細胞有著一套完善的機制控制著其生長速度，而這些機制大多數時候均會在癌細胞發發生的基因變異影響下作廢，促使癌細胞能夠無止境地生長及繁殖。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BYyi4h1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBYyi4h1.jpg&h=26c8fbd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當一個細胞需要繁殖的時候，細胞膜以及DNA是不可或缺的元件。<br />\n而在糖份分解的過程中，所涉及的代謝物均能參與細胞膜和DNA的製作。<br />\n<br />\n亦即是說，癌細胞不斷無止境地生長，導致內部位置沒有足夠氧氣，正好更能觸發更多糖份的攝取，繼續製作繁殖所需的細胞組件。<br />\n<br />\n但是，若氧氣沒能抵達癌細胞的話，那又如何能夠獲取營養呢？<br />\n<br />\n其中的一種渠道，就是從鄰近死去的細胞獲取。<br />\n<br />\n詳見可閱：<br />\n三十秒科學&ndash;化療效果參差的其中一道原因<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2378848\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2378848</a><br />\n<br />\n正因如此，腫瘤的核心大多是已死去的細胞，而其外部則是不斷繁殖的細胞。<br />\n而經過一段時間的繁殖後，早前的「外部」細胞便成為「核心」，成為鄰近細胞的糧食。<br />\n<br />\n日復如此，腫瘤亦得以無止境助大。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnXdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=a9cda569\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=0FWZMlR46yIxX%2BJDTULvnXdxOOSMRKapPz%2BIyyZ8sYw%3D&h=edc9e410\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。"},{"pid":"f83952c25d7f568fd38c4c1ce5cc41812ace6bac","tid":2416199,"uid":17064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T22:07:45.000Z","msg":"上年中左大腸癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bba78401a78704f406903d9ede0da667bdcd61ee","tid":2416199,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f83952c25d7f568fd38c4c1ce5cc41812ace6bac","tid":2416199,"uid":17064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T22:07:45.000Z","msg":"上年中左大腸癌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T22:09:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />現在情況OK？"},{"pid":"3067be6af27dce67d9d3e94408d0dfb0d5a6f5f2","tid":2416199,"uid":84588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T22:46:00.000Z","msg":"30秒睇到有冇個po嘅10分1"},{"pid":"90dc086ce95c40e51cd5830e029b51