1081","tid":2416199,"uid":120123,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T00:48:45.000Z","msg":"其實就算癌細胞嚮有氧的環境 &quot;大部分&quot; 癌都會增加糖份攝取。中間死左果d位，其實反而唔係好吸到糖份。<br />\n<br />\n如果你照過PET就知，因為其實佢係打radioactive glucose幫你照，通常如果你舊野真係有central necrosis，你axial slice會見到好似冬甩咁，外面光，中間黑。即係佢係得出面果部分食到d糖份。<br />\n<br />\n其他增加癌細胞糖份攝取的機制有: <br />\n1. 增加glucose transporter expression <br />\n2. 增加左angiogenesis，即係生多左血管去舊野度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T08:42:38.000Z","msg":"用外來的radioactive或者 florescence analog glucose，入面的癌細胞食唔到出面的glucose係非常合理，亦到證明咗無一個內循環&ndash;外面的癌細胞並唔會太有效率咁將glucose送入內部，而內部的癌細胞亦唔會將lactate送到外部俾有氧的癌細胞食用。<br />\n<br />\n但用外來radioactive glucose的話，係睇唔到內部癌細胞點利用macropinocytosis食死亡細胞體內的glucose，因為死亡細胞裡頭的glucose並無labelled。<br />\n<br />\n當然，用BrdU睇的話，大多數只有靠近血管的癌細胞處於活躍繁殖的階段。"},{"pid":"96fa4c71f4a8c53e14b175e8b440ab53b1ace47c","tid":2416199,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T16:42:55.000Z","msg":"幾好睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4ce11b53706663e7125c69ae0a51ec11a690de7","tid":2416199,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25a4fe4467d5035da59537805cbb9e08809fbd9d","tid":2416199,"uid":36995,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T00:39:29.000Z","msg":"人類有冇辦法完全唔食糖份"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T16:57:37.000Z","msg":"試下生酮再講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e91965665fbcb58e15776485adb7704750b1ff17","tid":2416199,"uid":49836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T17:36:36.000Z","msg":"想問下有無ref睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"094166b4b323f5cb7c273ad4a03b891c79ecb9c3","tid":2416199,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4ce11b53706663e7125c69ae0a51ec11a690de7","tid":2416199,"uid":141871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote